meaning_str.bing:
adj. 不快乐的；不幸福的；难过的；悲伤的
网络. 不高兴的；不幸的；不愉快的

不快乐的；不幸福的；难过的；悲伤的
不高兴的；不幸的；不愉快的

不快乐的；不幸的；不满的；悲伤的；沮丧的；郁闷的；忧郁的；烦恼的；不幸福的

1.en: "I was unhappy, I was eating the wrong stuff, I was doing the wrong things and now it's like the complete opposite, " she said.
1.cn: “我不开心，吃的不对，做的也不对。而现在一切恰恰相反。”她说。

2.en: Mary always love to take advantage of things. this time we done so fair. it has no weakness to exploit, no wonder she will be unhappy.
2.cn: Mary老是爱占便宜，这次这么公平，无机可乘，难怪她会不高兴。

3.en: The unhappy US-Pakistani shotgun marriage will continue, at least for a while longer.
3.cn: 美-巴之间因一时之需的勉强合作不会中断，至少要持续一段时间。

0.en: I had no idea you were unhappy. That's the thing: I'm not. I'm not unhappy at all. It's just... I don't know...
0.cn: 我不知道原来你爱得不开心。重点就在这，我没有不开心，我完全没有不开心，只是...

1.en: What? Don't sit in his spot. Fine. Happy? I'm not unhappy.
1.cn: 你说啥？不要坐他的专座。好吧，满意了？我没有不满意。

2.en: Tom believes you're unhappy. That's why you lash out as you do.
2.cn: 汤姆觉得你不开心，所以才那么发脾气。

3.en: You're unhappy, Grady. Why? May I speak candidly? Sure, go ahead.
3.cn: 你很不高兴，格雷迪，怎么回事？我能直言吗？当然，说。

4.en: My life is taken up with client maintenance these days. Why is everybody so unhappy?
4.cn: 最近我老是忙着维护客户关系，为什么每个人都这么不满呢？

5.en: I'm saying, if you were any other partner, I'd be as unhappy and competitive as I am now.
5.cn: 我是说，如果你是其他人，我会一样的好胜和不爽。

6.en: I have, yes. And this has made you unhappy? I'll not say that. But I want to do more with my life.
6.cn: 没错 ,这让你不高兴吗?没有,但我想拥有更大的成就.

7.en: Your parents have been unhappy ever since we've known them. Especially after that incident in Hawaii.
7.cn: 从我们认识他们开始，他们就一直很不快乐，特别是在夏威夷那件事之后。

8.en: Because of largely dependent by relativity, it can drive us do all kinds of thing that we are unhappy.
8.cn: 因为很大程度上取决于相对，它可以驱使我们做各种不喜欢的事。

9.en: Sanctions hit in a couple of hours. Deal with Secretary Durant or with some very unhappy billionaires.
9.cn: 再过几个小时制裁就要生效了。你要么和杜兰特国务卿谈要么对付几个愤怒的亿万富翁去吧。

10.en: I just don't want you to be unhappy. I mean it. Okay. All right. We'll come back. This is nice. It's very nice.
10.cn: 我只希望你能快乐。我说真的。明白。那就好。我们会再回来的。这儿很漂亮。非常漂亮。

11.en: It's not easy for me to visit this town. Were you really so unhappy? That's not what I'm saying. It's not what I meant. Well, then?
11.cn: 我不愿回到这座城市。你过得真那么不开心？这不是我要说的。我不是这个意思。那是什么意思？

12.en: Okay, just to be clear, roller skating was my idea, and I'm very unhappy that you turned it into a double date, and I hope you both fall on your asses and break your coccyxes.
12.cn: 我要把话说清楚了，滑旱冰是我的主意，而我对你们将其变成四人约会表示高度不满，我预祝你们都摔屁墩，摔断尾椎骨。
